title: 466 Tailored Tees
description:
MATERIAL: 97% Cotton, 3% Spandex. 

FIT: Fitted.

DESIGN: The basic tee, is designed with a tailored fit to accentuate your physique. This stylish and versatile tee is all about showcasing your aesthetics. By wrapping around the biceps and fitting snugly in the right areas, it effortlessly enhances your silhouette and adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Large. Weight: 185lb Height: 5'11.
